Module JavaDataStructures
Package JavaDS.Sorters

Class SuperSort<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • JavaDS.Sorters.SuperSort<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of data elements being sorted.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISorter<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BubbleSort, HeapSort, InsertionSort, MergeSort, QuickSort, SelectionSort
    public abstract class SuperSort<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISorter<T>
    A superclass for sorting algorithm classes that contains shared logic and functionality required by any given sorting algorithm that might extend it, such as storing and retrieving data and swapping data elements in a collection.
    Author:
    Tom Esser
